課程教材 Course Material
	    嚴格來說同調代數是一種善巧的數學語言，而不是一門數學理論。其發展源頭可追溯到在十九世紀末代數拓撲與抽象代數的發展，其源頭這兩門理論各自由Poincare與D. Hilbert發展出來。同調代數在第二次世界大戰後才確立為一個獨立數學分支。如今它已是數學及理論物理中一個深刻和重要的工具，並且在代數拓撲、交換代數、代數幾何、複幾何、代數數論、表示理論、與非交換幾何等領域上為不可缺少的工具。

課程會包括下列的基本內容:
Definition of categories, Examples
Functors and natural transformations, Examples
Equivalences of categories, Examples
Representable functors, Yoneda lemma, Examples
Adjoint functors. Examples 
Additive categories, abelian categories. Examples. 
Chain Complexes, Chain Homotopies , Mapping Cones, Long Exact Sequences,
Chain Homotopies, Projective and Injective Resolutions, Left/Right Derived Functors,δ-functors, Examples. 
The Homotopy Category, Triangulated Categories. 

如果時間允許我們會講授:
Localisation, Derived category
The derived category as a homotopy category
Total derived functors,
Spectral squence
     

參考書目 References
	    Weibel, Charles A. An introduction to homological algebra, Cambridge Studies in Advanced Mathematics, 38. Cambridge University Press, Cambridge, 1994.

Schapira(2011) Categories and Homological Algebra, webusers.imj-prg.fr/~pierre.schapira/lectnotes/HomAl.pdf

B. Iversen, Cohomology of Sheaves, Universitext, Springer, 1986.
     

